title: #288 - Josh Wolf, Joey Diaz, and Lee Syatt
description:
Josh Wolf, Comedian and Host of the new TV Show, "The Josh Wolf Show" on CMT starting June 11, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt live in studio.

This podcast is brought to you by:

Recorded live on 06/03/2015.
